#Text=Hello , Houston .
#Text=I am so thrilled to be here in the great state of Texas with one of America 's greatest , most devoted and most loyal friends , Prime Minister Modi of India .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=And Prime Minister Modi is doing a truly exceptional job for India and for all of the Indian people .
#Text=It is my immense privilege to be here with him today at this profoundly historic event .
#Text=We 're especially grateful to be joined by over 50,000 incredible members of our nation 's thriving , prospering , flourishing , and hardworking Indian American community .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=Just a few months ago in the largest democratic election in the history of our world , 600 million Indians went to the polls and voted overwhelmingly for Prime Minister Modi and his party .
#Text=Congratulations , Mr.
#Text=Prime Minister .
#Text=That 's a lot of people .
#Text=Earlier this week , I understand you marked another important milestone .
#Text=I know everyone here joins me in wishing you a very happy birthday .
#Text=Happy birthday .
#Text=I want to take a moment to address every resident of Houston effected by the recent horrible flooding .
#Text=The entire American nation is standing by your side .
#Text=We 're ready .
#Text=We love you .
#Text=We support you .
#Text=We will be there with you every single step of the way .
#Text=I just left the Coast Guard hanger at Ellington Field Joint Reserve Base where I was briefed on the Texas flooding .
#Text=We 're working with your great governor Greg Abbott , Lieutenant Governor Dan Patrick , Attorney General Ken Paxton and senators John Cornyn and Ted Cruz .
#Text=Thank you very much .
#Text=We 're working hard together .

#Text=My administration will not rest until you have fully recovered , restored , and rebuilt and I know you will come back with the same tremendous spirit that we have shown every single time , every time there 's been a problem .
#Text=It 's called " Houston strong . "
#Text=Prime Minister Modi and I have come to Houston to celebrate everything that unites America and India , our shared dreams and bright futures .
#Text=I 've also come to express my profound gratitude to the nearly 4 million amazing Indian Americans all across our country .
#Text=You enrich our culture , you uphold our values , you uplift our communities and you are truly proud to be American and we are proud to have you as Americans .
#Text=We thank you , we love you and I want you to know my administration is fighting for you each and every day .
#Text=I want to recognize US Ambassador to India Kenneth Juster and Minister Jaishankar of India .
#Text=Thank you very much .
#Text=Thank you both .
#Text=Thank you very much .
#Text=Thank you .

#Text=We 're also proudly joined by NASA Deputy Administrator Jim Morhard , Deputy Secretary Of Energy Dan Brouillette , Governor Matt Bevin of Kentucky , your state attorney general , Ken Paxton , a couple of very great senators .
#Text=Kevin , thank you .
#Text=Thank you all for being here .
#Text=Thank you ,
#Text=Kevin .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=We have a lot of senators .
#Text=We have a lot of Congress people .
#Text=There 's Mr. Brady , Congressman Brady .
#Text=He gave us a very , very nice tax cut folks .
#Text=Thank you ,
#Text=Kevin , very much .
#Text=Thank you all for being here .
#Text=Among the leaders here today for this remarkable celebration are many members of the House and Senate .
#Text=They 're all over the audience , including House majority leader , Steny Hoyer , and again , senators Cornyn , Cruz .
#Text=In my campaign for president , I promised all of that .
#Text=If we were elected , India would have a true and great friend in the White House and I can tell you , you have never had a better friend as president that President Donald Trump .
#Text=That I can tell you .
#Text=The prime minister knows that .
#Text=On this day , I 'm happy to report that the relationship between the United States and India is stronger than ever before .
#Text=The ties between our two nations are grounded in our common values and our shared commitment to democracy .
#Text=We are free nations with great faith and a fierce devotion to our national independence .
#Text=We are governed by the rule of law , guided by commitment to justice , and strengthened by our love of liberty .
#Text=Our two national constitutions both begin with the same three beautiful words , " We the People . "
#Text=That means that in America AMD
#Text=India alike , we honor , respect , trust , empower and fight for the citizens we proudly serve .
#Text=Under Prime Minister Modi 's leadership , the world is witnessing a strong sovereign and thriving Republic of India .
#Text=In a single decade , with the help of Prime Minister Modi 's pro-growth reforms , India has lifted nearly 300 million people out of poverty and that is an incredible number .
#Text=Incredible .
#Text=That 's incredible .
#Text=In the next decade , 140 million Indian households will rise to the middle class .
#Text=In both India and the United States , we 're seeing something really remarkable .
#Text=Our people are prospering like never before because we are slashing bureaucracy and cutting job killing red tape .

#Text=In the United States , thanks to our massive tax cuts and all of our great senators and congressmen and women that are here today and pro worker policies , our economy is breaking one record after another .
#Text=Since my election , we have created over 6 million new jobs .
#Text=We have created over 750,000 jobs right here in Texas and very importantly , that includes 70,000 new Texas manufacturing jobs .
#Text=They said that could n't be done .
#Text=Unemployment …
#Text=Think of this .

#Text=Unemployment in Texas is currently at the lowest rate ever recorded in the history of our country , and unemployment in the United States has just reached the lowest level in over 51 years and very soon we think that will be broken to be a historic number .
#Text=Unemployment among African Americans , Asian Americans , and Hispanic Americans have all reached their lowest levels in the history of our country .
#Text=Over the last two years , the unemployment rate among Indian Americans dropped by nearly 33 and one third percent .
#Text=Wages are rising , incomes are soaring , and inequality is falling at the fastest rate in many , many years .
#Text=In the past 12 months alone , the average worker has taken home $ 1,000 extra in rising wages and over $ 3,000 with tax cuts and all of the other things that we 've done .
#Text=And for the first time in history , most new hires of prime working age are minorities and women .
#Text=First time that 's ever happened .

#Text=Through our pledge to America 's workers , we have secured commitments for nearly 14 million employment and training opportunities for American workers done through our great American companies .
#Text=We passed the biggest tax cuts and the biggest tax reforms in the history of our country .

#Text=We slashed a record number of job killing regulations , giving the average American household more than $ 3,000 every year and never in the history of our country , no matter how long the presidency , have regulations been cut to this extent .
#Text=Everyday , the Indian American community is helping to strengthen our country and build our future .
#Text=Indian Americans are pioneering groundbreaking medicines to save countless lives .
#Text=They 're developing revolutionary technology that is changing the world and they 're founding new businesses that provide jobs to thousands of our fellow citizens .
#Text=Prime Minister
#Text=Modi , I look forward to working with you to make our nations even more prosperous than ever before .
#Text=And that 's what 's happening .
#Text=The economic miracles taking place today are just beginning .
#Text=Here in the United States , there has never been a better time to hire , invest , grow , and pursue your dreams .
#Text=Indian companies employ tens of thousands of Americans across a range of industries , including American steel .
#Text=In 2018 India 's JSW Steel announced that it would invest up to $ 500 million to revitalize a shuttered steel plant in the great state of Ohio .
#Text=And we welcome India 's growing investments right here in the Lone Star State .
#Text=Nations around the world are investing in the United States because they know we have the best economy and the best workers in the world .
#Text=They have never invested in our country like they are today .
#Text=And we want to thank everybody and India has never invested in the United States like it is doing today .
#Text=And I want to say it 's reciprocal because we 're doing the same thing in India .
#Text=On Tuesday , two Japanese companies , Toyota and Aisin , announced a combined investment of almost $ 800 million , which will create over 900 new jobs right here in Texas .
#Text=At the same time , we are working to expand American exports to India , one of the world 's fastest growing markets .
#Text=We are committed to ensuring the Indian people have access to the finest goods in the world , product stamped with a beautiful phrase , " Made in the USA . "
#Text=And very soon , India will have access to another world class American product , NBA basketball .
#Text=Wow , sounds good .
#Text=That sounds good .
#Text=Next week thousands of people will gather in Mumbai to watch the first ever NBA basketball game in India .
#Text=Am I invited , Mr. Prime Minister ?
#Text=I may come .
#Text=Be careful .
#Text=I may come .
#Text=When it comes to expanding our commercial relationship , no issue is more important than energy security .

#Text=For the first time ever , the United States is the number one producer of both oil and natural gas on planet earth and number one by far , with much of it coming right here from the great state of Texas .
#Text=That means more jobs , higher wages , and lower prices at the pump .

#Text=Yesterday , we were thrilled to hear about the Indian company Petronas pledge to purchase up to 5 million tons of LNG per year from the United States , which could lead to billions of dollars of LNG exports to India in the coming years .
#Text=And we have plenty of it .
#Text=Over the last year , crude exports to India have grown by 400 % and liquefied natural gas exports continue to soar at record numbers .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=These tremendous exports not only expand employment in America , but they increase freedom and security for India .
#Text=To keep our nation safe , the United States and India forging an even stronger security partnership .
#Text=US defense sales to India have also reached $ 18 billion over the past decade .
#Text=We make the greatest defense mechanisms and equipment anywhere in the world and India knows that well .
#Text=We 're looking forward to concluding several new defense deals very soon .
#Text=There are a lot of them in the works .
#Text=Here in America , we 're creating the United States Space Force and we 're working closely with India to enhance space cooperation .
#Text=In November , the United States and India will demonstrate a dramatic progress of our defense relationship , holding the first ever tri-service military exercise between our nations .
#Text=It 's called Tiger Triumph .
#Text=Good name , it 's a good name .
#Text=Very good name .
#Text=Today , we honor all of the brave American and Indian military service members who work together to safeguard our freedom .
#Text=We stand proudly in defense of liberty and we are committed to protecting innocent civilians from the threat of radical Islamic terrorism .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=Both India and the United States also understand that to keep our communities safe , we must protect our borders .
#Text=Since taking office , my administration has launched a far - reaching effort to improve screening and vetting of applications for entry .
#Text=We are working hard to ensure that those who would threaten our security are denied admission into our country and we are enhancing our vetting efforts like - …
#Text=country , and we are enhancing our vetting efforts like never before , not even close .
#Text=We 're doing it on a daily basis , and we 'll soon be setting records in every one of the aspects of border security .
#Text=Border security is vital to the United States .
#Text=Border security is vital to India .
#Text=We understand that .
#Text=We are further taking unprecedented action to finally secure our southern border and stop illegal immigration .
#Text=I want to thank the president of Mexico , who right now has 27,000 soldiers on our southern border .
#Text=It 's been incredible what 's taken place in a short period of time .
#Text=Illegal immigration is deeply unfair to millions of wonderful legal immigrants who work hard , pay their taxes , follow our rules , and obey our laws .
#Text=Yet there are those in Washington who would raid your healthcare to …
#Text=Free benefits .
#Text=They want to fund free benefits to those who enter our country illegally .
#Text=We do n't want to do that .
#Text=We do n't want to do that .
#Text=Because if we do n't do it , they wo n't come .
#Text=I will never allow politicians to take away your healthcare or give it to illegal immigrants .
#Text=My administration believes our first duty is to the highest loyalty of all .
#Text=We must always be for the American people , whether it 's African - American , Hispanic - American , Indian - American .
#Text=We are going to take care of our citizens first .
#Text=We are going to take care of our Indian - American citizens before we take care of illegal immigrants that want to pour into our country .

#Text=We want to build a nation where every family , immigrant and US - born , can live in a safe community with access to great school , work in a job you love , and have the best chance to reach the American dream .
#Text=We love the American dream .

#Text=Just in concluding , I want to say that America has always been a nation of pioneers and patriots , risk - takers and free thinkers , and dedicated workers who have honed a trade , mastered their field , and teach their children to always give their very , very best .
#Text=Every day Indian - Americans help write the story of American greatness , and everyone here today has a crucial part to play in building an even grander and greater American and Indian future .

#Text=To help achieve that exciting vision , we are strengthening our cherished bonds with the nation of India , and we are proving the awesome power of democracy and unlimited potential of free people .
#Text=Together , we will continue to deepen the ties between our nations .
#Text=We will honor the faith of dignity of our citizens , and we will achieve incredible advancements for our people , for our children , and for the world .
#Text=We will discover new cures and save millions of lives .
#Text=We will advance cutting - edge technologies and lift millions and millions of people out of poverty .
#Text=We will pioneer new frontiers in space , working together , raising the sights of humanity .
#Text=We will uphold our values , defend our liberty , and control our destiny .
#Text=The United States and India will make our nations stronger , our people wealthier , our dreamers bigger , and our future brighter than ever before , and it wo n't even be close .
#Text=I want to thank everybody for being here .
#Text=I want to especially thank a great man and a great leader , the leader of India , Prime Minister Modi , my friend .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=God bless you all .
#Text=God bless India , and God bless America .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=Now I would like to invite onto this stage in front of this incredible group of unbelievable people Prime Minister Modi , who 's going to give us some of his wisdom .
#Text=His wisdom is indeed great .
#Text=Thank you all very much .
#Text=It 's been a great honor to be with you .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=Thank you .
